    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-06-09</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-07-07T21:25:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Pension Preservation and Portability Act of 2005 - Amends the Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974 (ERISA) and the Internal Revenue Code to require all defined benefit pension plans, including hybrid plans such as a cash balance plan, to comply with certain rules, in cases of reduction in accrued benefits because of attainment of any age, in order to be deemed nondiscriminatory as to age.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
